Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drop the pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If we stop, it's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:37.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,We're passing through the abandoned station.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Please brace for impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:23.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,What you need to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:27.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's not some tool that will\Nkeep you hidden and safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:32.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's the power to fight the Corpses{Kabane} without fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:04.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,Twenty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,...the people of Japan{Hinomoto}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:09.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,...have locked themselves in fortified stations out of fear of the Corpses{Kabane}.
Comment: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,...fear of the Corpses{Kabane}...
Comment: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:09.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,...drove the people of Japan{Hinomoto} to take shelter in stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:12.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,They abandoned their pride and fellow man...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,...and run away{ fled}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The suicide bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us what you're made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull it! {already}Pull it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:39.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Can we really be proud of our survival...\Nthat's predicated on sacrificed our own?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:44.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,And we lose not only the lives of our friends.
Comment: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:44.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,Their lives aren't all we lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:47.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,I want the power to defeat the Corpses{Kabane}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'm... so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Warriors{bushi} held them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...another station get overrun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They said the supplies are late.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.00,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,590)}I guess the front line fell back again.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,590)}How long is this place going to last?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,590)}{Hey,}Stop it, don't say that!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,590)}What if a Warriors{bushi} heard you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Running late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.00,Alt,,0,0,0,,Watch your calculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:04:59.90,Alt,,0,0,0,,Plate 3 needs more adhesive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Heeeey, Ikoma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How did yesterday go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It should have plenty of pressure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with using\Nnormal lead shots again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because then it'd be the same\Nas the Warrior{bushi}'s steam guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It will just get repelled by\Nthe Corpse{Kabane}'s heart cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we need jet bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We need more penetrating power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're going to use that to fight\Nthe Corpses{Kabane} instead of the Warriors{bushi}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be insane or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you up the explosives?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, because you just increased\Nthe cavity in the last tune-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I skip a step?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,At least finish your work here first...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Ayame-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,From the Yomokawa family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to check everything myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't it Ayame-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my father's steam gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's having some problems, so I was\Nhoping someone could take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:16.00,Alt,,0,0,0,,We would be happy to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayame-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the Warriors{bushi} princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikoma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here and help Ayame-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your chance, hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to become a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't like having to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayame-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...where will you be pointing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The west gate is opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Iron Fortress{Koutetsujou} is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Iron Fortress{Koutetsujou} should be coming tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Iron Fortress{Koutetsujou}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree Fortress{Fusoujou} is supposed to come tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Two Railfort{Hayajiro}s in one day...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, wasn't the Iron Fortress{Koutetsujou} supposed to arrive tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayatani Station has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,With less stops to make,\Nof course {it makes sense }it would arrive earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the inspection box!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if anyone's been bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they're about to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They search for bite marks to determine\Nif they have been infected by a Corpse{Kabane}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If they find one, they throw them in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what the authorities always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well of course they do.
Comment: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, can you blame them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That one might be infected.
Comment: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They could be incubating the infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, start the maintenance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the carotid artery is thicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So the virus really does pass through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare to find this good of a specimen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're breaking the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't some curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We both know it!
Comment: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that this isn't some curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kid of a bigwig?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You there, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The exit is the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even children have to go through inspect—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a fool would judge a book by its cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what my brother always\Ntold me, {Mr. }Mustache-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She is my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the boss here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kensho, head of\Nthe Yomokawa Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Lord }Yomokawa-dono, thank you\Nfor your hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimon-sama, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have read your letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We would like to take you\Nto our mansion first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not going to be inspected?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Corpse{Kabane}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a wound!
Comment: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been bitten!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A Corpse{Kabane}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not a Corpse{Kabane}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Surround and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, it's not a bite!
Comment: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, I'm not one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's saying he's not a Corpse{Kabane}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we can trust him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Those suspected of being a Corpse{Kabane}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,are to be locked up for three\Ndays and kept under watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the ones who made the rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This matter doesn't concern a lowly steam smith!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to tell you that you're pointing\Nyour guns at the wrong targets!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Corpse's{Kabane}{hearts}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he have them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's died...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't a Corpse{Kabane}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You aren't even ashamed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Being so afraid of everything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For losing your sanity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are some lofty words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A privilege afforded to you because of the\Nguaranteed safety the Warriors{bushi} provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fight too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurusu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm close to finishing the steam g—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw him in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be a Corpse{Kabane}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Defending order is also a Warrior{bushi}'s duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The order...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...is it?
Comment: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}You're both headed to Diamond Citadel{Kongokaku}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}Then, the {Lord }Warlord{Shogun}-sama is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}No, not {at this time}yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why the two of us are going alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's June.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost time, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the corpse gatherer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nameless{Mumei}{Anon}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nameless{Mumei}{Anon}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that {your }a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know that the guy\Nfrom before, wasn't a Corpse{Kabane}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't just ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's something\Nwrong with being normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it{ do you mean}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's normal to be\Nscared of the Corpses{Kabane}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,People are generally frightened cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They can do nothing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They can do nothing\Nbut kill others out of fear?
Comment: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They have no choice but kill others out of fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unthinkable to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot lose your humanity to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikoma is a {freaking }dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,590)}Getting all worked up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,590)}What a self-righteous idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,590)}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's something I couldn't do even if I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking back to a Warriors{bushi} like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes him stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here! It's the Tree Fortress{Fusoujou}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right on time this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey! }It's going too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Raise the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What{ happened}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Corpses{Kabane}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Corpses{Kabane}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...the tocsin{alarm bell}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Corpses{Kabane} are here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,I need to get my piercing gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking these too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nameless{Mumei}{Anon}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They have broken through the west gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole place is lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to the Iron Fortress{Koutetsujou}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Iron Fortress{Koutetsujou}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wait, y}You're not...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you abandoning this station?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give the signal when the\NIron Fortress{Koutetsujou} has been secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come when you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Corpses{Kabane} react to blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off your clothes immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Corpse{Kabane} are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you have to show that\Nyou don't have wounds on your body!
Comment: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Prove that you don't have any marks on your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Ikoma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He took the bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,I won't fail this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,I've increased the explosives this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My piercing gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...bore right through its heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My{ gun}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it{ this}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Iron Fortress{Koutetsujou}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nameless{Mumei}{Anon}-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You will have to continue on alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Diamond Citadel{Kongokaku}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...and please await the\NYoung Master's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,May karma smile upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:55.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's not a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:57.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,I just need to make sure the virus doesn't reach my brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's been five years!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:11.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,For whose sake I was working...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,...to be able to fight the Corpses{Kabane}...?!
Comment: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:13.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,All the work I put in to finally be able to fight the Corpses{Kabane}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:37.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'm{ not}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,{I'm }...not the same as I was then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:44.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,...will never run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,...again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:10.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:14.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,I will become someone I can be proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:46.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will remember that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:50.10,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Losing myself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:57.50,op/ed,,0,0,0,,In steam
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:06.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Countless mistakes are made
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:11.85,op/ed,,0,0,0,,When I can't see anything ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:14.50,op/ed,,0,0,0,,You said
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:20.05,op/ed,,0,0,0,,"Ask your own burning blood"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:23.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Answer my beat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:29.90,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Corpseless{Kabaneri} of the Iron Fortress
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:33.70,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Stand up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:38.15,op/ed,,0,0,0,,And slam everything onto the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:43.50,op/ed,,0,0,0,,My soul is devoted to my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:46.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Burn your life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:52.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Change the world
